and, according to a notification from the burgomaster of Cologne, the administrators of the zoological garden of that city have arranged to furnish in reciprocation for some black swans and for some contributions yet to be forwarded, select varieties of fowls, doves, water birds, and some hares and remarkable kind of rabbits.
